[I] A portable viewer for Microsofts ITSS/CHM files

[T] Xchm is a cross-platform GUI front-end to chmlib to view Microsofts
[T] ITSS/CHM files.
[T]
[T] Originally written for UNIX systems (Linux, *BSD, Solaris), xCHM has been
[T] since ported to Mac OS X and Windows.
[T]
[T] Xchm can show the content tree if one is available, print pages, change
[T] font face and size, remember bookmarks, display a searchable index, and
[T] search for words in the current page and the whole book.

[U] https://github.com/rzvncj/xCHM

